<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" href="/src/favicon.png" type="image/png">
    <title>ShareNote</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="page-shell">
        <div class="ad-banner">
            <button class="ad-nav ad-nav-prev" aria-label="Previous ad">❮</button>
            <div class="ad-carousel" id="adCarousel">
                <div class="ad-item">
                    <img src="/src/saniova.png" alt="Saniova Blog" class="ad-image">
                    <div class="ad-content">
                        <div class="ad-text-wrap">
                            <span class="ad-tag">Sponsored</span>
                            <h3>Step Into the Future of AI - Saniova</h3>
                            <p>Explore futuristic blogs, AI trends, automation ideas, and next-generation tech insights built for creators and developers.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ad-click">
                            <a href="https://rsantosh.com.np" class="ad-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Explore</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ad-item">
                    <img src="/src/saniova2.png" alt="Saniova Insights" class="ad-image">
                    <div class="ad-content">
                        <div class="ad-text-wrap">
                            <span class="ad-tag">Featured</span>
                            <h3>The AI Shift Nobody Is Ready For</h3>
                            <p>AI vs AGI isn’t just another tech debate. Discover how the future of intelligence could change jobs, creativity, and human potential forever..</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ad-click">
                            <a href="https://rsantosh.com.np/blog/the-ai-shift-nobody-is-ready-for-ai-vs-agi-explained/" class="ad-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Read Article</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ad-item">
                    <img src="/src/saniova3.png" alt="Saniova Tutorials" class="ad-image">
                    <div class="ad-content">
                        <div class="ad-text-wrap">
                            <span class="ad-tag">New</span>
                            <h3>Fresh Ideas. Future Thinking.</h3>
                            <p>Dive into the latest articles on AI, coding, productivity, automation, and the digital future — updated with modern insights and tech perspectives.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="ad-click">
                            <a href="https://saniova.com/blog/" class="ad-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Start Now</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="ad-nav ad-nav-next" aria-label="Next ad">❯</button>
            <div class="ad-dots">
                <span class="ad-dot active" data-index="0"></span>
                <span class="ad-dot" data-index="1"></span>
                <span class="ad-dot" data-index="2"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <main class="hero">
            <div class="hero-copy">
                <span class="eyebrow">ShareNote</span>
                <h1>Fast notes in a sleek cyan workspace.</h1>
                <p>Type a note name, open your file, and edit in a polished, futuristic editor.</p>

                <form id="titleChange" method="post" class="hero-form">
                    <label class="visually-hidden" for="filesName">Note name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="filesName" name="title" placeholder="Enter note name" autocomplete="off" required>
                    <button type="submit">Open note</button>
                </form>

                <p class="hero-hint">Use letters, numbers, or hyphens. Press Enter or click Open note.</p>
            </div>

            <aside class="hero-panel">
                <div class="panel-card">
                    <h2>ShareNote</h2>
                    <p>Minimal note files, maximum clarity.</p>
                    <div class="panel-grid">
                        <div>
                            <span>Keep it simple</span>
                            <strong>One file at a time</strong>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span>Built for focus</span>
                            <strong>Clean cyan theme</strong>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>

        
        </main>
        

    </div>

    <script src="/index.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
